%}

### Post 단건 조회 (A)
GET {{host}}/api/v1/posts/{{postId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Post 목록 조회 (A)
GET {{host}}/api/v1/posts
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Post 수정 (A)
PUT {{host}}/api/v1/posts/{{postId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "수정된 제목",
  "content": "수정된 내용"
}

### Post 삭제 (A)
DELETE {{host}}/api/v1/posts/{{postId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

